Package: libcmaesr
Title: R Interface to 'libcmaes'
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bernd", "Bischl", , "bernd_bischl@gmx.net", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6002-6980")),
    person("Martin", "Binder", , "mlr.developer@mb706.com", role = "aut")
  )
Copyright: See the file COPYRIGHTS for libcmaes copyright details
Description: A lightweight R interface to the 'libcmaes' C++ library for Covariance Matrix Adaptation
  Evolution Strategy (CMA-ES). It allows for the optimization of black-box functions using the CMA-ES algorithm
  and its variants. Includes a vendored copy of libcmaes (LGPL-3+); see inst/COPYRIGHTS.
License: LGPL-3
URL: https://github.com/mlr-org/libcmaesr
BugReports: https://github.com/mlr-org/libcmaesr/issues
